{"tid":485720,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[FBI]大陸直播平台小學女生掀衣露體","createTime":"2017-12-01T08:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T14:54:49.000Z","uid":44916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5702788abeb4cc343bc545e5e373cb3de3ceb0c6","tid":485720,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"內地直播平台「美拍」被揭發有小學生等未成年人直播脫衣露體，從網上片段可見，有兒童在直播期間掀起上衣，有直播觀眾留言慫恿主播脫衣。有玩直播的小學生自言，常看到下流的說話，但看多了就不覺憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒訪問到自稱出生於2005年的小學生，她直言裸體直播不是為賺錢，是為了好玩，更稱「我在我們班粉絲最多」。<br />\n<br />\n據「美拍」人員表示，平台設有圖像及封面識別，「現在應該不會讓未成年人新註冊」，亦限制了已有的未成人帳戶直播功能，平台將特別監控。華中師範大學生命科學學院教授彭曉輝指，有關現象對女生成長是個非常嚴重的事件，「她（女生）不明真相」，認為除父母對此有責任外，直播平台應負有最大責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171201/s00004/1512103247451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171201%2Fs00004%2F1512103247451&d=R5uB2q%2F6rUkR92WZqqw0yW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c938a172\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171201%2Fs00004%2F1512103247451&h=25aa3610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171201/s00004/1512103247451</a>"},{"pid":"ba9d1bb80e7975517ae089233cd52d632ee130bf","tid":485720,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8da9a9342983c2d9f287b7be196a52392c39518","tid":485720,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ced7f03443889fa173e65495a8a079a12c92188","tid":485720,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"小美麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /